{
  "stem": "10905.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "At the same time, her father was exhibiting at the Near East Fair in the fairground, which is now still the fairgrounds in-- in Tel Aviv.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I mean, it was just sand, not dirt, sand.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was just beach and sand and heat and the flies and-- and my mother said no.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She's never going to live there in no-- no way, shape, or form.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That was in '34.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "By '47, she had two children, and we came here because it was now impossible to go.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And she said, well, we're going to make our life over here.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Now, the rest of our family that survived, her two brothers, my aunt , and my maternal grandmother, the first chance that Tito let the Jews go from Yugoslavia to Israel, they immigrated to Israel.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "My wife's another story.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "My wife also went to Israel with her family.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They went back to Yugoslavia and-- because they were searching, I guess, for her grandparents.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And also, her father wanted to go back, and he was a pharmacist.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They went back.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And then in '48, they went on the first ship that allowed to take children, because she had a young brother who was just born.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so on the first ship that took children, they went, and they went to Israel.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And although we had known each other as children, of course she didn't remember me.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She was two years old, and I was seven.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I-- of course I didn't remember her.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But when I was in Israel for the first time in 1965, I was driving in an automobile with my mother and one of her cousins.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I said, you know, I know that couple.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it was my future father-in-law and his wife.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
